HEADWORD: Plastering
<hw>Plas"ter*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Same as
<er>Plaster</er>, <pos>n.</pos>, 2.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act or process of overlaying with
plaster.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A covering of plaster; plasterwork.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Plasterly</ent>⟦br⟧
